      • storageKey

        public FlowParser storageKey​(java.lang.String storageKey)
        Description copied from interface: Parser
        Sets a static storage key for all art objects created by this parser.

        This is needed if the created ArtObjectContext should persistently store the data under the given storage key.

        Make sure you create separate parser instances for each storage key.
